(2/2) It’s always hard for us to leave, & we know that needs persist. But #FRF was #fortunate to be able to provide #freefuel for #police and #fire departments, ambulances, city generators, & close to 1700 families in need.

text: #HurricaneFlorence, lessons from Harvey. If all electronic comms are down, have a way to signal for rescue. Spraypaint, flags, flares, banners, fluorescent vests, *anything* to signal that you need rescue. Otherwise that helicopter is going to have a hard time seeing you.
text_html: #HurricaneFlorence, lessons from Harvey. If all electronic comms are down, have a way to signal for rescue. Spraypaint, flags, flares, banners, fluorescent vests, *anything* to signal that you need rescue. Otherwise that helicopter is going to have a hard time seeing you.
